ccashx - ccash command client
=============================
ccashx is a command line client for remote ccash servers.

Installation
------------
ccashx comes with a Makefile and config.mk file for configurable building and
testing.  Edit the latter to match your local setup (ccashx is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default, you may need to modify your $PATH).

ccashx can be installed with the following command (run as root):

    make install

